{
  "stem": "9102.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She never worked herself.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So, you know, I don't know exactly what the money was.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But we didn't have any real shortage of money.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But I really as a boy didn't have much money, pocket money, at all.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And, so, whatever I did in the summer we made money, you know, as boys-- picking cherries, working here and there, and then go on a holiday.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But we [? lived from-- ?] the Dutch government kind of paid everything.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And, you know, I had to go to university that was out of town.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And so they paid my transportation.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they paid-- I was in a room there with some people, what they paid for and all this.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Yeah, so I have no complaints about that at all.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And she-- she really had, you know, lived from that, because she never did any work.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "However, then we got to Winnipeg in '58.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And, well, but it-- you know, [INAUDIBLE] we decided-- I was gonna get married.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So I started to save.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So then she had to start working too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So that's when she ended up, the funny part, in Winnipeg with a family, Jewish family, helping in the-- you know, in the house, with the house work.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
